    "bio": "Pixcels Themes is a modern AI Automation Agency helping businesses streamline time-consuming tasks through intelligent automation. We build practical AI solutions—from automated workflows and Shopify integrations to custom chatbots and tailored AI agents—that replace manual work with smart, self-running systems. Our focus is simple: make businesses faster, more efficient, and ready for the AI-powered future",
